Name: My Cute Commissar
About the game: ☭My Cute Commissar☭ is a satyrical historical visual novel with “match-3” type of gameplay. Take part in the political struggle in the 1920’s communist Russia! Take the power in your own hands and bring Trotsky or Stalin to ruling position! Get to know the leaders of Russian communist movement intimately. Ignite the flames of the world-wide revolution or build communism in one country! The choice is yours! ♥ ☭Stalin☭ – young beautiful lady following the ideas of communism, but she doesn’t believe the idea of the world-wide revolution. She wants to get power into her own hands and build communism in one country with industrialization and Great Purge♥ ☭Trotsky☭ – naive girl obsessed with dreams of permanent revolution and freedom for the proletariat. You may call her a fanatic, but she surely doesn’t seem like one. Power and personal gain doesn’t interest her at all. Her only goals: military communism and freedom for all the oppressed people, no matter the cost!♥ Features: A love story in the 1920’s Russian setting! Multiple endings Cute Stalin and even cuter Trotsky A classic novel with Match-3 gameplay Lofi hip hop by G374 This game does not contain non-tolerance, any symbols of any political organizations and anything like that. Only love and mutual understanding. Make Match3, not war ♥
